OL,3,CEpstein, pizzagate and UFOs: Videos of
OL,4,CClinton deposition released
OL,6,FThe full depositions of former US
OL,7,FPresident Bill Clinton and former
OL,8,FSecretary of State Hillary Clinton
OL,9,Fhave been released by the House
OL,10,FOversight Committee.
OL,12,FThe pair were questioned for over four
OL,13,Fhours each last week over their
OL,14,Frelationships with convicted
OL,15,Fpaedophile Jeffrey Epstein and what
OL,16,Fthey knew about his crimes. They are
OL,17,Fsome of the highest-ranked officials
OL,18,Fto have ever been deposed by Congress.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
