OL,3,CEpstein, pizzagate and UFOs: Videos of
OL,4,CClinton deposition released
OL,6,FHowever, the newly released videos of
OL,7,Fthe closed-door proceedings, released
OL,8,Fon Monday night, show the Clintons
OL,9,Ffrequently veering off track and
OL,10,Fhaving to be reigned in by their
OL,11,Flawyers.
OL,13,FWatch the key moments from the
OL,14,FClintons' testimonies on Epstein
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
