OL,3,CEpstein, pizzagate and UFOs: Videos of
OL,4,CClinton deposition released
OL,6,FDuring their individual testimonies,
OL,7,Fthe Clintons both distanced themselves
OL,8,Ffrom Epstein, with the former
OL,9,FDemocratic president denying any
OL,10,Fknowledge of his crimes, and Hillary
OL,11,Frepeatedly saying she did not recall
OL,12,Fever meeting him.
OL,14,FTheir depositions come as American
OL,15,Flawmakers are trying to meet demands
OL,16,Ffor a reckoning over Epstein, who
OL,17,Fkilled himself in 2019 in New York
OL,18,Fwhile facing charges for sex
OL,19,Ftrafficking and abusing underage girls.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
