OL,3,CEpstein, pizzagate and UFOs: Videos of
OL,4,CClinton deposition released
OL,6,FThe deposition of Hillary on Thursday
OL,7,Fwas hardly underway when it was put on
OL,8,Fpause after a photo taken by
OL,9,FRepublican Congresswoman Lauren
OL,10,FBoebert was sent to a conservative
OL,11,Finfluencer who posted it online.
OL,13,FIt violated the committee's protocol
OL,14,Ffor depositions and threatened for a
OL,15,Fmoment to derail the session.
OL,17,F"I am done with this if you guys are
OL,18,Fdoing that," Hillary said. "You can
OL,19,Fhold me in contempt from now until the
OL,20,Fcows come home."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
