OL,3,CEpstein, pizzagate and UFOs: Videos of
OL,4,CClinton deposition released
OL,6,FThe two sides reached an agreement to
OL,7,Fcontinue, but as the afternoon wore
OL,8,Fon, Hillary started to lose her
OL,9,Fpatience with Republicans' repeated
OL,10,Fquestions about whether she had any
OL,11,Fconnections to Epstein.
OL,13,F"I am so tired of answering that
OL,14,Fquestion," she said at one point.
OL,16,FBill Clinton's relationship with
OL,17,FEpstein
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
