OL,3,CEpstein, pizzagate and UFOs: Videos of
OL,4,CClinton deposition released
OL,6,FOn Friday, Bill faced questions both
OL,7,Ffrom Republicans and Democrats about
OL,8,Fphotos of the former president that
OL,9,Fhave been released as part of the
OL,10,FEpstein files.
OL,12,FThe former Democratic president said
OL,13,Fhe first remembered meeting Epstein
OL,14,Fwhen he flew aboard the financier's
OL,15,Fprivate jet in 2002 for the Clintons'
OL,16,Fhumanitarian work, and that they
OL,17,Fparted ways the year after.
OL,19,F"We were friendly, but I didn't know
OL,20,Fhim well enough to say we were
OL,21,Ffriends," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
