OL,3,CEpstein, pizzagate and UFOs: Videos of
OL,4,CClinton deposition released
OL,6,FEpstein visited the White House
OL,7,Fnumerous times during Clinton's
OL,8,Fpresidency, and there are photos of
OL,9,Fthem shaking hands. Clinton told
OL,10,Flawmakers he did not recall those
OL,11,Finteractions.
OL,13,FIn response to questions about a photo
OL,14,Fthat showed him in a pool with a woman
OL,15,Fwhose face was redacted, the former
OL,16,Fpresident said he did not know the
OL,17,Fwoman and did not engage in sexual
OL,18,Factivity with her.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
