OL,3,CEpstein, pizzagate and UFOs: Videos of
OL,4,CClinton deposition released
OL,6,FHe said the photo was from a trip to
OL,7,FBrunei for charitable work, and
OL,8,Fseveral people in their travel party
OL,9,Fwere swimming.
OL,11,FHe also said that he was not aware
OL,12,Fthat one young woman who was
OL,13,Fostensibly working as a masseuse and
OL,14,Fgave him a neck massage on one flight
OL,15,Fwas in fact a victim of sexual abuse.
OL,17,F"There's nothing that I saw when I was
OL,18,Faround him that made me realize he was
OL,19,Ftrafficking women," he told the
OL,20,Fcommittee.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
