OL,6,FHe said he had once visited Epstein's
OL,7,Ftownhouse in New York City, but said
OL,8,Frepeatedly he had never visited
OL,9,FEpstein's private island or other
OL,10,Fproperties.
OL,12,FAsked by Republicans whether they had
OL,13,Ftalked about young women or girls
OL,14,Ftogether, Clinton said: "No."
OL,16,FClinton acknowledged he maintained a
OL,17,Fcloser relationship with Ghislaine
OL,18,FMaxwell, Epstein's former girlfriend
OL,19,Fand confidant.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
