OL,6,FBut he maintained that it was largely
OL,7,Fbecause of close mutual connections.
OL,8,FHe also said "she has to be punished"
OL,9,Ffor her conviction on sex trafficking
OL,10,Fcharges.
OL,12,F50th birthday message
OL,14,FBill was made to read aloud a message
OL,15,Fhe had written for Jeffrey Epstein's
OL,16,F50th birthday book.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
