OL,3,CEpstein, pizzagate and UFOs: Videos of
OL,4,CClinton deposition released
OL,6,F"It's reassuring isn't it, to have
OL,7,Flasted as long, across all the years
OL,8,Fof learning and knowing, adventures
OL,9,Fand errors and still to have your
OL,10,Fchildlike curiosity, the drive to make
OL,11,Fa difference and the solace of
OL,12,Ffriends," he read.
OL,14,FWhen asked if the "errors" were in
OL,15,Freference to Epstein's crimes, the
OL,16,Fformer president said, "Absolutely
OL,17,Fnot".
OL,19,F"Anyone who has lived 50 years has
OL,20,Fmade mistakes as well as progress," he
OL,21,Ftold the committee.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
