OL,6,FConspiracy theories
OL,8,FBoth Bill and Hillary Clinton were
OL,9,Fquestioned on well-known conspiracy
OL,10,Ftheories surrounding Epstein and his
OL,11,Fdeath.
OL,13,FWhen asked if he believed Epstein
OL,14,Fkilled himself in prison, the former
OL,15,Fpresident replied, "I only know what
OL,16,Fthe medical finding was. None of us
OL,17,Fknow. We weren't there."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
