OL,3,CEpstein, pizzagate and UFOs: Videos of
OL,4,CClinton deposition released
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Hillary Clinton was asked
OL,7,Fwhether there were emails in the case
OL,8,Ffiles on Epstein that referenced
OL,9,F"pizzagate" ` a conspiracy theory
OL,10,Falleging the Democratic Party insiders
OL,11,Fharbored child sex slaves in a
OL,12,FWashington pizza parlor.
OL,14,FHillary responded by saying, "I can't
OL,15,Fbelieve you're even referencing it"
OL,16,Fand reminding her that the conspiracy
OL,17,Ftheory resulted in a man bringing a
OL,18,Fgun to a Washington restaurant.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
