OL,11,FHowever, Republicans did find some
OL,12,Fagreement with Hillary when it came to
OL,13,Fproviding more disclosure on what
OL,14,Finformation the government has
OL,15,Fgathered on UFOs.
OL,17,FShe agreed that any releases should
OL,18,Fnot include national security
OL,19,Finformation but that "this is an issue
OL,20,Fof real importance to so many people."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
