OL,6,FCalls for Trump to face the committee
OL,8,FDuring Hillary's opening statement,
OL,9,Fshe urged politicians to ask US
OL,10,FPresident Donald Trump about Epstein
OL,11,Fwhile under oath.
OL,13,F"If this committee is serious about
OL,14,Flearning the truth about Epstein's
OL,15,Ftrafficking crimes, it would not rely
OL,16,Fon press gaggles to get answers from
OL,17,Four current president on his
OL,18,Finvolvement; it would ask him directly
OL,19,Funder oath about the tens of thousands
OL,20,Fof times he shows up in the Epstein
OL,21,Ffiles," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
