OL,6,FWhen asked directly if Trump should
OL,7,Fface the committee, she said the US
OL,8,Fpresident "has been held civilly
OL,9,Fliable for sexual assault by a jury of
OL,10,Fhis peers... That is behavior that
OL,11,Ffits a pattern if one were looking for
OL,12,Fa pattern."
OL,14,FShe added: "Given what's in the files
OL,15,Fand given past and prior conduct, he
OL,16,Fwould be on my witness list."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/17
